{"type":"finding","iteration":14,"id":"S2-06A-deterministic-similar-node-query","dimension":"D1","focus":"S2-06","summary":"Kasper uses a deterministic similarity helper before any model call: exact match, substring score, exact word-overlap, and longer-word fuzzy overlap with Levenshtein thresholds. Our coverage graph query layer should expose similar-node discovery for duplicate FINDING/CLAIM names before LLM consolidation.","sourceRefs":[".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/utils.ts:13",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/utils.ts:18",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/utils.ts:21",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/utils.ts:33",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/utils.ts:51",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/utils.ts:68",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/utils.ts:71",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/constants.ts:55",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/constants.ts:56",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/constants.ts:57",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/constants.ts:58",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/constants.ts:59"],"targetFile":".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/coverage-graph/coverage-graph-query.ts","supportFiles":[".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/tests/unit/coverage-graph-query.vitest.ts"],"portDifficulty":"med","tag":"quick-win","whyItHelps":"Lets graph queries find duplicate findings and claims with cheap deterministic scoring before expensive semantic review."}
{"type":"finding","iteration":14,"id":"S2-06B-bounded-alias-cache","dimension":"D1","focus":"S2-06","summary":"Kasper memoizes incoming weakness strings to canonical map keys and caps the alias cache at 500 entries, dropping the oldest 250 on overflow. Our coverage graph query layer can use the same bounded alias memo for repeated similarity checks over graph node names.","sourceRefs":[".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:125",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:126",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:638",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:639",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:640",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:641",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:651",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:652",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:653",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:655"],"targetFile":".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/coverage-graph/coverage-graph-query.ts","supportFiles":[".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/tests/unit/coverage-graph-query.vitest.ts"],"portDifficulty":"med","tag":"quick-win","whyItHelps":"Keeps repeated duplicate-discovery queries cheap during long research runs without introducing unbounded cache growth."}
{"type":"finding","iteration":14,"id":"S2-06C-two-stage-consolidation-candidates","dimension":"D1","focus":"S2-06","summary":"Kasper performs cheap incremental map aggregation first, then runs LLM consolidation only as an explicit sweep over sorted weakness lists. It replaces state only when the model returns a valid shorter list and otherwise returns the original weaknesses. Our coverage graph query layer should expose cheap and leftover candidate clusters, leaving model invocation to a later workflow stage.","sourceRefs":[".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:422",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:426",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:427",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:431",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:432",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:433",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:454",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/scorer.ts:64",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/scorer.ts:74",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/scorer.ts:166",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/scorer.ts:170",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/scorer.ts:256",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/scorer.ts:260"],"targetFile":".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/coverage-graph/coverage-graph-query.ts","supportFiles":[".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/scripts/query.cjs",".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/deep-loop/post-dispatch-validate.ts"],"portDifficulty":"hard","tag":"deep-rewrite","whyItHelps":"Avoids making every graph import model-dependent while still creating a clean handoff for ambiguous duplicate consolidation."}
{"type":"finding","iteration":14,"id":"S2-06D-guarded-reversible-aliases","dimension":"D1","focus":"S2-06","summary":"Kasper prevents false merges by requiring category compatibility before threshold matching, and its decrement path finds the best mergeable key before reversing counts. Our graph duplicate query should constrain candidates by namespace and node kind and return scores/aliases for deliberate downstream repair rather than mutating graph rows directly.","sourceRefs":[".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/utils.ts:237",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/utils.ts:243",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/utils.ts:246",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/utils.ts:248",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/utils.ts:250",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/utils.ts:252",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:659",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:663",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:667",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:669",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:670",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:776",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/state.ts:790"],"targetFile":".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/coverage-graph/coverage-graph-query.ts","supportFiles":[".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/tests/unit/coverage-graph-query.vitest.ts"],"portDifficulty":"med","tag":"quick-win","whyItHelps":"Prevents accidental merges across SOURCE/TARGET/FINDING nodes and gives repair tooling a reversible candidate list."}
{"type":"observation","iteration":14,"id":"observation:S2-06:query-surface-has-no-similarity-path","summary":"The current coverage graph query module exposes gap, contradiction, provenance, unverified-claim, and hot-node queries, but no similar-node or duplicate-candidate query. This makes query-time duplicate discovery the smallest target for porting kasper's cheap-first merge pattern.","reference":[".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/coverage-graph/coverage-graph-query.ts:130",".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/coverage-graph/coverage-graph-query.ts:221",".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/coverage-graph/coverage-graph-query.ts:265",".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/coverage-graph/coverage-graph-query.ts:320",".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/coverage-graph/coverage-graph-query.ts:393"],"target":".opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/lib/coverage-graph/coverage-graph-query.ts"}
